# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Types   : feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, perf, ci, revert
# Scope   : config, handler, worker, repo, ui, logger, main
# Subject : imperative mood, max 50 chars, no period at end
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Contoh yang BAIK:
#   feat(worker): add exponential backoff on API timeout
#   fix(repo): prevent nil pointer in GetBedAvailability
#   refactor(config): extract security config into nested struct
#   test(handler): add error path coverage for beds endpoint
#
# Body (opsional) — jelaskan KENAPA, bukan apa yang diubah:
#
#
# Footer (opsional) — Breaking changes, issue ref:
# BREAKING CHANGE: <deskripsi>
# Closes #<issue-number>
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
